channel.title: Who wants a champions online key?
channel.description:
I have a retail key, from the boxed edition of the game, unattached to an account, allowing you to create an account + have 30 days of free playtime.
Buying selling and trading is not allowed on these forums, so I will not partake in it.
I'll just say, that I'm not gonna give the key away for nothing, and I'd really like some WoW gametime, be that someone paying on my account or giving me a gamecard, and I have no interest in playing champions online.
and my email is mopman@gmail.com
EDIT: oh btw, champions is $39.99 on amazon.com, wow time is a lot less ;) EDIT++: oh yeah, the champs key is worldwide (they dont have regions) but my wow account is eu - american cards work ;) IM STILL NOT TRADING
ps im transparent as an iron bar
